# Project Overview

Full-stack web application: FastAPI backend + Vue 3 frontend, Docker Compose orchestration, Nginx reverse proxy, PostgreSQL, Prometheus/Grafana monitoring.

## Commands

- `make setup` — create .env files from examples
- `make dev-up` / `make dev-down` — start/stop dev services
- `make dev-test` — run pytest in Docker
- `make dev-lint` — ruff check + format --check + mypy
- `make dev-format` — auto-fix with ruff
- `make dev-shell` — bash into server container
- `cd client && npm run test:unit` — Vitest unit tests
- `cd client && npm run lint` — ESLint

## Architecture

- Backend at `server/`, frontend at `client/`, nginx configs at `nginx/`
- Dev: `docker-compose.yaml` + `docker-compose.override.yaml` (port 5746)
- Prod: `docker-compose.yaml` + `docker-compose.prod.yaml`
- Nginx routes: `/` → frontend, `/api/*` → backend, `/health`, `/ready`, `/metrics`
